    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Seve Ballesteros: Flair Without the Noise",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Seve's style lived in the details. A navy sweater with white piping. A shirt collar popped just slightly out of a V-neck. He didn't chase flash, but he understood presence. His European roots brought a tailored edge to American fairways.</p><p>If Seve were playing today, there's a good chance he'd be wearing <strong>Greyson</strong> or <strong>J.Lindeberg. </strong>This are brands that build their aesthetic around elevated simplicity and movement-conscious design.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
