    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Erik van Rooyen: The Rockstar Golfer",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Erik van Rooyen has singlehandedly made joggers, facial hair, and untucked shirts look respectable on Tour. His look says \"musician accidentally joined a PGA event,\" and we mean that in the best way possible. He blends edge with performance and pulls it off.</p><p>If Arnie was the prototype, Erik is the remix. You'll catch him in <strong>Bogey Boys</strong>, <strong>G/FORE</strong>, and anything that blurs the line between streetwear and sport.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
