    "text_6": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "So... Who Wins?",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>That's the trick. You don't have to choose.</p><p>The past gave us polish. The present gave us personality. Together, they've shaped a new kind of golf style, one that still respects the game but isn't afraid to challenge what it <em>should</em> look like.</p><p>At TRENDYGOLF, we live for that evolution. Whether you're channeling Arnie's clean classics or leaning into Jason Day's cropped chaos, we've got the brands and pieces to help you find your lane and swing in it confidently.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
